    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level 2005 Porsche 911 Carrera S. This 997.1 features the 3.8L M97 flat-six, delivering 355 hp with a surgical 7,200 RPM redline. The IMS bearing has been proactively replaced with a ceramic upgrade, ensuring mechanical longevity. The 6-speed manual gearbox utilizes a factory short-shift kit for precise, tactile engagement, while the PASM-equipped chassis provides active damping for optimized lateral stability. With zero fluid seepage, perfect paint depth, and a pristine undercarriage, this specimen is mechanically and aesthetically flawless. A turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
