      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the 'used' car experience. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish thanks to a professional-grade multi-layer ceramic coating; there are zero stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state\u2014the premium leather upholstery is supple and completely free of creases or wear, still retaining its original factory aroma. Every electronic feature functions flawlessly, and the mechanicals are equally impressive, backed by a comprehensive, gap-free service history performed exclusively by authorized technicians. From the pristine alloy wheels with brand-new Michelin tires to the spotless undercarriage, this car is for the collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection. It drives as tightly and smoothly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
